    <item>
      <title>Ternium 首席执行官称墨西哥需要明确的私人投资规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ternium-ceo-says-mexico-needs-clear-rules-for-private-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特尔尼姆公司首席执行官马克西莫·维多亚 (Maximo Vedoya) 表示，墨西哥必须制定明确的私人投资规则，以便利用近岸外包机会并支持总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ternium-ceo-says-mexico-needs-clear-rules-for-private-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰银行称中国风力涡轮机在欧洲尚不可行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-wind-turbines-aren-t-yet-viable-in-europe-abn-amro-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行 (ABN AMRO Bank NV) 项目和基础设施融资董事总经理丽莎麦克德莫特 (Lisa McDermott) 表示，如果欧洲风电场选择使用可能更便宜的中国风力涡轮机，那么向其提供贷款目前尚不可行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/chinese-wind-turbines-aren-t-yet-viable-in-europe-abn-amro-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:06:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长纳格尔担心特朗普获胜将导致经济增长放缓、通胀加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-s-nagel-fears-slower-growth-faster-inflation-if-trump-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员约阿希姆纳格尔警告称，如果唐纳德特朗普再次当选美国总统，欧洲经济可能面临增长大幅放缓和通胀加剧的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/ecb-s-nagel-fears-slower-growth-faster-inflation-if-trump-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
