    <item>
      <title>美联储降息推动 Brevan 创下 2022 年以来最佳月度回报率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/brevan-posts-best-monthly-return-since-2022-on-fed-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储降息幅度超过一些交易员的预期，Brevan Howard Asset Management 9 月份回报率为 5.1%，为 2022 年以来的最佳月度回报率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/brevan-posts-best-monthly-return-since-2022-on-fed-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 16:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙面包店 Europastry 考虑缩减 IPO 规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/spanish-baker-europastry-is-said-to-consider-reducing-ipo-size</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，西班牙烘焙公司 Europastry SA 正在考虑是否缩小其计划的首次公开募股规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/spanish-baker-europastry-is-said-to-consider-reducing-ipo-size</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 15:35:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股市因缺乏中国新刺激措施而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/em-currency-traders-zero-in-on-us-election-driving-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国在备受关注的新闻发布会上未能公布进一步的重大刺激措施，新兴市场股市暴跌，引发人们对近期上涨行情的可持续性产生怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-08/em-currency-traders-zero-in-on-us-election-driving-volatility</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂缓推出新刺激措施 油价在强劲上涨后暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，中国国家主席习近平结束了备受期待的发布会，未公布新的刺激措施，引发整个市场的避险情绪，油价随之暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 23:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 涨幅达 13%，Mag Seven 股价上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大科技公司的股价上涨推动股市上涨，市场从一个月以来最糟糕的交易日中反弹。随着交易员们仔细阅读美联储官员的讲话，美国国债的暴跌势头停止。油价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 22:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
